Title: A Representation of the Virasoro Algebra via Wigner-Heisenberg Algebraic
  Technique to Bosonic Systems
Authors: E. L. da Gra\c{c}a, H. L. Carrion and R. de Lima Rodrigues
Comments: Revised version. Revtex, 7 pages, no figures. This work was presented
  in the XXII Brazilian National Meeting on Particles and Fields
  (October/2001), to appear in Braz. J. of Phys., 33, 1 (2003)
Report-no: Preprint ``Notas de F\'\i sica'' CBPF-NF-012/02
Journal-ref: Brazilian Journal Physics, 33, 1 (2003)
\\
  Using the Wigner-Heisenberg algebra for bosonic systems in connection with
oscillators we find a new representation for the Virasoro algebra.
